OL,3,CDonald Trump arrives in Europe ahead
OL,4,Cof G7 summit after US-Iran deal agreed
OL,6,FDonald Trump has arrived in Geneva for
OL,7,Fthe G7 summit, a day after the US
OL,8,Fpresident said an agreement was
OL,9,Freached to end the war in Iran.
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer will be among the
OL,12,Fworld leaders joining the US president
OL,13,Fat Evian-les-Bains in the French Alps
OL,14,Ffor the three-day summit, where the
OL,15,FIran deal and the continuing conflict
OL,16,Fin Ukraine will be among the issues on
OL,17,Fthe table.
OL,26,@uD@Drb
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
