OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781576262
OL,3,CDonald Trump arrives in Europe ahead
OL,4,Cof G7 summit after US-Iran deal agreed
OL,6,FThe reopening of the Strait of Hormuz
OL,7,Fwill likely be top of the agenda, with
OL,8,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron
OL,9,Fsaying a joint operation between the
OL,10,FUK and France to restore freedom of
OL,11,Fnavigation in the Gulf region could
OL,12,Fbegin "two or three days" after the
OL,13,Fdeal is signed.
OL,15,FIran's Deputy Foreign Minister Kazem
OL,16,FGharibabad said they will refrain from
OL,17,Fany attacks in the crucial waterway
OL,18,Funtil the deal is signed, with Friday
OL,19,Ffloated as a potential date to sign
OL,20,Fthe deal in Switzerland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
