CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781576262
OL,3,CDonald Trump arrives in Europe ahead
OL,4,Cof G7 summit after US-Iran deal agreed
OL,6,FThe US military has already begun
OL,7,Fsearching for Iranian mines in the
OL,8,FStrait, and an extensive post-conflict
OL,9,Fdemining operation may be needed.
OL,11,FInternational businesses will also
OL,12,Fwant to ensure the conflict is over
OL,13,Fand the Strait is safe before they
OL,14,Fstart operating in the region again.
OL,15,FIt will likely be months until
OL,16,Fbusiness returns to normal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
