OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781576262
OL,3,CDonald Trump arrives in Europe ahead
OL,4,Cof G7 summit after US-Iran deal agreed
OL,6,FLebanon will also be high on the
OL,7,Fagenda, with Israel insisting it will
OL,8,Fnot withdraw from land it has seized
OL,9,Fsince the latest incursion began in
OL,10,FMarch.
OL,12,FIran has tied the interim deal over
OL,13,Fthe war to halting Israel's attacks on
OL,14,FHezbollah in Lebanon. Hezbollah has
OL,15,Fnot commented on the deal.
OL,17,FAll G7 nations have urged Israel to
OL,18,Fhalt its attacks on Lebanon, with
OL,19,FFrance in particular being extremely
OL,20,Fcritical of its actions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
