OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781576262
OL,3,CDonald Trump arrives in Europe ahead
OL,4,Cof G7 summit after US-Iran deal agreed
OL,6,FThe group's leaders have also said
OL,7,Fthey will discuss Ukraine, with more
OL,8,Fthan a dozen people killed in recent
OL,9,Fdays in Ukraine and Russia amid
OL,10,Fongoing strikes between the two sides.
OL,12,FThe G7 includes France, the United
OL,13,FStates, Canada, Germany, Italy, Japan
OL,14,Fand the United Kingdom. Guest nations
OL,15,Fat this summit include Brazil, Egypt,
OL,16,FIndia, Kenya, South Korea, Qatar,
OL,17,FSyria, Ukraine, and the United Arab
OL,18,FEmirates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
