OL,3,CDonald Trump arrives in Europe ahead
OL,4,Cof G7 summit after US-Iran deal agreed
OL,6,FUkrainian President Volodymyr
OL,7,FZelenskyy is expected to join the
OL,8,Fsummit on Tuesday.
OL,10,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FStarmer's attendance also comes amid
OL,16,Funcertainty around his future as prime
OL,17,Fminister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
