PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781576262
OL,3,CDonald Trump arrives in Europe ahead
OL,4,Cof G7 summit after US-Iran deal agreed
OL,6,FStarmer was also critically weakened
OL,7,Fby the shock resignation of defence
OL,8,Fsecretary John Healey last week over
OL,9,Fwhat he said was the failure to
OL,10,Fprovide adequate funding for the long-
OL,11,Fdelayed Defence Investment Plan.
OL,13,FWith security issues so high on the
OL,14,Fagenda, the fact that Starmer was so
OL,15,Fopenly accused of underfunding the
OL,16,FBritish military from within his own
OL,17,Franks, when nations like the US and
OL,18,FGermany are pouring money into theirs,
OL,19,Fwill tarnish his image on the world
OL,20,Fstage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
